window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Bunny girls make everything better.</p> <p>At least, that's been Hunter's experience. After getting stranded in another dimension and losing a good chunk of his memory, the soldier from Earth finds that he has landed in the midst of absolute societal collapse.</p> <p>This new world is tearing itself apart and Hunter has found himself charged with the protection (and care) of four aggressively attractive women who, save for a pair of rabbit ears and a fluffy tail, look human. Four beautiful women who seem very eager to be in his company.</p> <p>There are worse places to be stranded.</p> <p><i>Down the Rabbit Hole Collection One collects the first four episodes of the series, and includes two bonus short stories that take place from the girls' perspective.</i></p>"; 
